snippet.title: Michelle Walks
snippet.description:
There is a zero tolerance policy against trolls on this channel. If you are a troll, you are not welcome here. You will be blocked from commenting on livestreams and on videos, and if you moderate on this channel, please feel free to remove any comment that you deem to be trolling. There will be no discussion, no considerations and no second chances. 

All views my own & not representative of affiliations I hold in the real world. My personal opinions, however strong, about people, places, events, information and other, should be taken in the good spirit in which they are intended. Where I am discussing serious topics, I am interpreting research and data based on my own views. My commentaries on other channels and people are opinion not stated as fact.
